<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yṭlq qlby</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 (yṭlq qlby fyk mdyḥạaⁿ wtnbʿ sẖfty tsbyḥạaⁿ)2
 ḥbk ysby kl kyạny (lạ ạ̉rḍy̱ ạ̹lạk msyḥạaⁿ)2
 (klk ḥlw msẖthyạt wklạmk ʿsl wḥyạẗ)2
 ạ̉ʿṭyk mqạlyd lsạny(ky tḥlw fyk ạlklmạt)2
 (lys kmạl ạ̹lạ mnk lys jmạl ybʿd ʿnk)2
 mhmạ ạrtfʿt fyk ạ̉gẖạny (tbqy̱ ạ̉bʿạd lạ tḥky̱)2
 (qrbny mnk lky ạ̉bqy̱ bjwạrk yạ nbʿy ạlạ̉nqy̱)2
 sẖkẖṣk mwḍwʿ ạlgẖymạn(bk wḥdk llmjd sạ̉rqy̱)2</lyrics>
<author>smyr ạlsẖwmly, slạm ʿmysẖ</author>
<hymn_number>6318</hymn_number>
</song>